# Vercel — environment variables
# Set these in the Vercel project dashboard (or via `vercel env`).
#
# VITE_API_BASE tells the frontend where the Rust backend lives.
# In dev, requests are proxied through Vite (see vite.config.ts) so this is
# empty. In a Vercel deploy, the frontend runs on https://your-app.vercel.app
# and the API is on the VPS, so we set the absolute origin here.

# Production
VITE_API_BASE=https://www.your-domain.com
